        <circle cx="16.5" cy="14.5" r="1" />
      </svg>
    `,
    href: "/en/services/parking/",
  },
  {
    title: "Lodging",
    description: "Comfortable rooms and spaces for couples, families or groups in a cozy environment.",
    icon: `
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path d="M3 18v-7h18v7" />
        <path d="M7 11V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v3" />
        <path d="M3 18v2M21 18v2" />
      </svg>
    `,
    href: "/en/services/lodging/",
  },
  {
    title: "Wellness Area",
    description: "Pool, sauna, steam room and hydromassage for moments of relaxation and wellness.",
    icon: `
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path d="M3 15c1.2 0 1.8 1 3 1s1.8-1 3-1 1.8 1 3 1 1.8-1 3-1 1.8 1 3 1 1.8-1 3-1" />
