        <circle cx="12" cy="19" r="1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none" />
      </svg>
    `,
    href: "/en/services/internet/",
  },
  {
    title: "Buffet Breakfast",
    description: "Start the day with delicious and varied options to enjoy with family or as a couple.",
    icon: `
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path d="M4 14h16" />
        <path d="M6 14v2a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h8a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-2" />
        <path d="M8 10h8" />
        <path d="M9 6h6" />
      </svg>
    `,
    href: "/en/services/breakfast/",
  },
  {
    title: "Events",
